{"tid":818430,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Sony XZ3 香港10月發表啦","createTime":"2018-09-14T06:02:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T07:07:14.000Z","uid":116493,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bee07558592fbaffa030efd2a3d4bcb6d8f3270a","tid":818430,"uid":116493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T06:02:10.000Z","msg":"Sony 早前於 IFA 2018 上發表了新一代旗艦級手機 Xperia XZ3，該機手機在外型上改用全新的設計，並首度採用雙曲面屏幕設計，令人有一種全新的感覺。SONY Mobile 今日正式宣佈 Xperia XZ3 將於10月4日正式在香港發表，屆時將公佈該機的上市日期及建議零售價，對這個 SONY 新旗艦的網友就要留意。<br />\n<br />\n新一代 Xperia XZ3 將機身厚度由 Xperia XZ2 的 11.1mm 減至 9.9mm，進一步令外觀更好看。此外，還採用 18:9比例的6吋 QHG+ HDR OLED 2K 屏幕，至於機身背面就設有指紋識別器及撘載了主鏡頭。<br />\n<br />\n至於在規格上，Sony Xperia XZ3 採用6吋 QHD+ HDR OLED屏幕，這塊屏幕加入了X-Reality for mobile 將一般畫質提升至近乎HDR質素。此外，在屏幕兩邊首度加入AI側屏感應介面，與HTC Edge Scene 相似，用戶只需輕拍兩下XZ3的左右兩側任何一方屏幕邊框，介面便會智能地預計您所想使用的應用程式。處理器就配備 Snaapdragon 845平台，仍舊內建 6GB RAM + 64GB ROM，搭載1900萬像AI功能主鏡頭及1300 萬像自拍鏡頭，電池容量為3300mAh等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mobilemagazinehk.com/2018/09/sony-新旗艦將於10月初正式在港發表！.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mobilemagazinehk.com%2F2018%2F09%2Fsony-%E6%96%B0%E6%97%97%E8%89%A6%E5%B0%87%E6%96%BC10%E6%9C%88%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%9C%A8%E6%B8%AF%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%A8%EF%BC%81.html&d=prQzaSRThAvUF1LR3lMCpNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=7f561247\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mobilemagazinehk.com/2018/09/sony-新旗艦將於10月初正式在港發表！.html</a>"},{"pid":"81f11e4dfa4501bea69b203f19e9db6ed8e73143","tid":818430,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T06:10:14.000Z","msg":"留番架仔自己用黎打飛機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n買an機梗係買大韓民族Samsung <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af375aa6b6abb255670215cfbd85b9b436d79d14","tid":818430,"uid":14476,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"81f11e4dfa4501bea69b203f19e9db6ed8e73143","tid":818430,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"ci